condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, A. 1 | Description :Establish the Program Steering Committee. | Due Date :30-Sep-2007
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, A. 2 (a) | Description :Establish a Program Coordination Unit at the national level. | Due Date:30-Dec-2007
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, A. 3 (a) | Description :Establish a management team at provincial level in each ParticipatingProvince. | Due Date :31-Dec-2007
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, A. 5 | Description :Ensure each Participating Province establish a provincial Project account. |Due Date :31-Dec-2007
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, B. 2 | Description :Submit an annual work plan and budget for each Part of the Project for reviewand concurrence. | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, B. 3 | Description :Prepare a communications and awareness strategy. | Due Date :31-Dec-2007
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, B. 4 | Description :Undertake a baseline survey of the Project performance indicators for eachpart of the Project. | Due Date :31-Mar-2008
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, B. 5 | Description :Prepare a document setting out the scope of the Project audit. | Due Date:30-Jun-2008
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, B. 7 (a) | Description :Ensure, though MAL, that each Participating Province develops an AnnualAgriculture Service Program | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, B. 8 (c) | Description :Perform bi-annual reviews of all SEF Grant transactions and provideresults in the Project Report and publish, at least six monthly, a list of all SEF Grant transactions in the preceding period. |Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec I, C.5. | Description :Prepare an Integrated Pest Management Plan | Due Date :31-Dec-2010

Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec II, A. 2 | Description :Prepare a report on the progress in carrying out the Project and setting outmeasures to ensure the efficient carrying out of the Project. | Due Date :30-Sep-2009
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec II, B. 2 | Description :Prepare interim unaudited financial reports covering the quarter. | Frequency:Quarterly
Finance Agreement :Sch 2, Sec II, B. 3 | Description :Submit the audited Financial Statements for each period no later than sixmonths after the end of the period. | Frequency :Yearly
